# Ability Name			Unique Key							Category of Ability		Type															Define					Description																																																			Auto Armor Prof						Auto Shield Prof										Auto Weapon Prof								Add 											Bonus DC													Add to base move			Modify VAR				Damage Reduction												Source Page		Aspects
Oracle Domain granted		KEY:Divine Oracle ~ Oracle Domain granted		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassAbility.SpecialQuality.Divine Oracle Class Feature.Class Feature									DESC:Oracle Domain granted																																																																																																																															SOURCEPAGE:p.36
Scry Bonus				KEY:Divine Oracle ~ Scry Bonus			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassAbility.SpecialQuality.Supernatural.Divine Oracle Class Feature.Class Feature							DESC:A divine oracle adds a +1 sacred bonus to the save DC of all her divination (scrying) spells.																																																																													BONUS:DC|DESCRIPTOR.Scry|1|TYPE=Sacred	BONUS:DC|SUBSCHOOL.Scrying|1|TYPE=Sacred																									SOURCEPAGE:p.36
Prescient Sense			KEY:Divine Oracle ~ Prescient Sense			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassAbility.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary.Divine Oracle Class Feature.Class Feature							DESC:Beginning at 2nd level, if a divine oracle makes a Reflex saving throw against an attack that normally inflicts half damage on a successful save, she instead takes no damage, since her prescience allowed her to get out of the way faster. This form of evasion always works for the divine oracle.																																																																																		SOURCEPAGE:p.36
Divination Enhancement		KEY:Divine Oracle ~ Divination Enhancement	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassAbility.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary.Divine Oracle Class Feature.Class Feature							DESC:Beginning at 3rd level, a divine oracle may roll twice and take the better result when using divination spells such as augury and divination.																																																																																																											SOURCEPAGE:p.36
Immune to Surprise		KEY:Divine Oracle ~ Immune to Surprise		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassAbility.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary.Divine Oracle Class Feature.Class Feature							DESC:At 10th level, the divine oracle's sensitivity to danger is so great that she is never surprised. She can always take a standard action during a surprise round, unless she is physically restrained from doing so.																																																																																															SOURCEPAGE:p.36
Trap Sense				KEY:Divine Oracle ~ Trap Sense			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassAbility.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary.Divine Oracle Class Feature.Class Feature	DEFINE:TrapSenseBonus|0			DESC:At 2nd level, the divine oracle gains an intuitive sense that alerts her to danger from traps, giving her a +%1 bonus on Reflex saves to avoid traps and to AC against traps.|TrapSenseBonus																																																																																																			SOURCEPAGE:p.36	ASPECT:NAME|Trap Sense +%1|TrapSenseBonus
Uncanny Dodge			KEY:Divine Oracle ~ Uncanny Dodge			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassAbility.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary.Divine Oracle Class Feature.Class Feature.Uncanny Dodge							DESC:Starting at 4th level, a divine oracle gainst the ability to react to danger before her senses would normally allow her to do so. She retains her Dexterity modifier to AC regardless of being flat-footed or struck by an invisible attacker. (Though she does still loose it if she is immobilized).																																																																																		SOURCEPAGE:p.36
Improved Uncanny Dodge		KEY:Divine Oracle ~ Improved Uncanny Dodge	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassAbility.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary.Divine Oracle Class Feature.Class Feature.Uncanny Dodge	DEFINE:UncannyDodgeFlankingLevel|0	DESC:At 6th level and higer, the divine oracle can no longer be flanked, since she can react to opponents on opposite sides of her as easily as she can react to a single attacker. This denies a rogue the opportunity to sneak attack unless the rogue is level %1 or higher.|(UncannyDodgeFlankingLevel+4)																																																																																	SOURCEPAGE:p.36

# Favored Soul
Weapon and Armor Proficiency	KEY:Favored Soul ~ Weapon and Armor Proficiency	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Favored Soul Class Feature.SpecialQuality														DESC:Favored souls are proficient with all simple weapons, with light and medium armor, and with shields (except tower shields). A favored soul is alos proficient with his diety's favored weapon.  Although a favored soul is not proficient with heavy armor, wearing it does not interfere with her spellcasting.	AUTO:ARMORPROF|ARMORTYPE=Light|ARMORTYPE=Medium	AUTO:SHIELDPROF|SHIELDTYPE=Buckler|SHIELDTYPE=Heavy|SHIELDTYPE=Light	AUTO:WEAPONPROF|DEITYWEAPONS	AUTO:WEAPONPROF|TYPE=Simple																																																		SOURCEPAGE:p.8
Weapon Focus			KEY:Favored Soul ~ Weapon Focus			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Favored Soul Class Feature.SpecialQuality														DESC:At 3rd level, a favored soul gains the Weapon Focus feat with her deity's favored weapon. If the character already has that feat, she can choose a different one.																																																							ADD:ABILITY|FEAT|VIRTUAL|Weapon Focus ~ FS,Weapon Focus Bonus																																										SOURCEPAGE:p.8
Energy Resistance			KEY:Favored Soul ~ Energy Resistance		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Favored Soul Class Feature.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary											DESC:At 5th level, a favored soul chooses an energy type and gains resistance 10 against that type. At 10th level and 15th level, the character gains resistance 10 against another energy type of her choosing.																																																																																																	SOURCEPAGE:p.8
Weapon Specialization		KEY:Favored Soul ~ Weapon Specialization		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Favored Soul Class Feature.SpecialQuality														DESC:At 12th level, a favored soul gains the Weapon Specialization feat with her deity's favored weapon. If she already has that feat, she can choose a different one.																																																							ADD:ABILITY|FEAT|VIRTUAL|Weapon Specialization ~ FS,Weapon Specialization Bonus																																							SOURCEPAGE:p.10
Wings					KEY:Favored Soul ~ Wings				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Favored Soul Class Feature.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary											DESC:At 17th level, a favored soul gains wings and can fly at a speed of 60 feet (good maneuverability). A good-aligned favored soul grows feathered wings, and an evil-aligned favored soul gains batlike wings. A favored soul who is neither good nor evil may choose either type of wings.																																																												BONUS:MOVEADD|TYPE.Fly|60	BONUS:VAR|Maneuverability|3															SOURCEPAGE:p.10
Damage Reduction			KEY:Favored Soul ~ Damage Reduction			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Favored Soul Class Feature.SpecialQuality.Supernatural												DESC:A 20th-level favored soul gains damage reduction. If the character is lawful-aligned, the damage reduction is 10/silver. If the character is chaotic-aligned, the damage is 10/cold iron. A favored soul who is neither lawful nor chaotic may choose either type of damage reduction.																																																																						DR:10/silver|PREALIGN:LG,LN,LE,NG,TN	DR:10/cold iron|PREALIGN:CG,CN,CE,NE	SOURCEPAGE:p.10

